name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sqagi: AI Car Summary for Cars.com

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: AI Assistant generates summarized pros and cons of cars on cars.com

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The AI Car Summary for Cars.com extension provides users with AI-generated summaries of car listings on cars.com. It highlights the pros, cons, summary, and important warnings about each car, helping users make informed decisions. The extension leverages advanced AI capabilities to analyze car details and generate accurate summaries, ensuring a personalized and efficient car browsing experience.
